{"tid":2334830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟多國切斷英國交通往來 物流可能都成問題","createTime":"2020-12-21T11:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:49:12.000Z","uid":286206,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"17c11ac7280b8e029f38ab468e1b6e657a0f1631","tid":2334830,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566475-20201221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566475-20201221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d5092024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566475-20201221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f176bf7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566475-20201221.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n英國太誠實 中國一定扮無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國發現變種新型冠狀病毒後，多國禁止英國航班入境，法國更暫停同英國的海陸空交通48小時，包括有人隨行的貨運。<br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜將召開緊急內閣會議商討對策。歐盟成員國代表亦會在布魯塞爾開會，協調措施。<br />\n<br />\n英國的食品供應及英國產品出口會受影響。英國第二大連鎖超市說，若未能盡快與歐洲大陸恢復交通往來，超市貨架幾天內就會開始缺短部分蔬果。<br />\n<br />\n貨運業呼籲民眾冷靜，表示將與政府密切聯繫，確保聖誕和新年期間的新鮮疏果供應。<br />\n<br />\n另外，運輸大臣夏博思保證，限制措施不會影響由比利時運送新型冠狀病毒疫苗入境。"},{"pid":"03104f6ca76254b1a9579554c17b9fcfc9349c98","tid":2334830,"uid":333488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"17c11ac7280b8e029f38ab468e1b6e657a0f1631","tid":2334830,"uid":286206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1566475-20201221.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1566475-20201221.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzOBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d5092024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk